result.title: Tokyo Revengers: Christmas Showdown (2023) Eng Subbed || 720p [60MB] || 1080p [100MB] ~ {Ep09}
result.description:
The Christmas Showdown Arc, popularly referred to as the Black Dragon Arc, will be adapted for the second season. It covers Chapters 78–121 of the manga if you wish to read it yourself. Considering that Season 1 deleted the Valhalla arc, which ended at Chapter 73, you might prefer to begin from Chapter 74.

Takemechi was saved by Kazutora before he was shot in the season finale. He tells Takemechi after making his getaway that Toman turned evil after Mikey was inspired by Black Dragon. Later that evening, none other than Naoto abruptly detained Takemechi. He leads him into a questioning area where he demonstrates to him the effects of his prior deeds on their chronology.
